getOrganizerEntriesCount().notice: Get number of entries created by given message sender

isRegisteredForEntry(uint256).notice: Checks if message sender is registered for given event

userdoc.notice: Contract owner gets paid small fee for each SignUpEventEntry created. Users can register to SignUpEventEntry. Once due date passes, SignUpEventEntry organizer can randomly choose selected participants of the event.
